{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Defenders Guild</h2>Immerse yourself in an exciting battle to protect the realm in Defenders Guild, an thrilling fantasy tower defense game! Instead of towers, you'll recruit and lead brave adventurers in the fight against hordes of evil enemies. Do you have what it takes to lead the best guild of defenders and safeguard the land from the growing darkness?<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1. Tactical Strategy: Strategically place your adventurers along the enemy's path to make the most of their unique abilities. Choose wisely, as each adventurer has their own strengths and weaknesses.<br></li><li>2. Variety of Adventurers: Recruit a diverse cast of adventurers with different combat styles and magical powers. From spellcasting mages to skilled archers and courageous warriors, there's a character for every situation.<br></li><li>3. Challenging Enemies: Battle flying enemies soaring above your defenses, swift creatures attempting to quickly pass through, enemies with magical armor or enemies who grant buffs to others! Be prepared to adapt to each challenge.<br></li><li>4. Add prioritary targets! : Set prioritary targets to each of your adventurers to go deep in your strategies.</li></ul>Defenders Guild combines strategy, action, and fantasy in a captivating gaming experience. Get ready to lead your guild to victory and become the bravest and most powerful defender the realm has ever known!<br><br>This game is a personal project developed by a single developer. Please feel free to contact me and share your comments, ideas and critiques \u2013 your opinion matters to me.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Debuff!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2586110/5753663bfcfe3f4bc3758f1a18e729beedf50417.jpg"},{"name":"Nerf them!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2586110/4eb5ffb91b30b8133d5d23ccd61701a480a24f29.jpg"},{"na